    "en": {
      "title": "National Fuel Card System Impossible: Harsha De Silva",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Chief Financial Officer Harsha de Silva has said that the plan introduced today (16) to get weekly fuel under the quota system for vehicle owners is impossible.",
        "He mentioned on his Twitter page that it has been a few hours since the introduction of the website for making reservations for getting fuel weekly under the quota system, and despite several attempts, he has not been able to register through the appropriate website. (a)"
      ],
